name: Unidentified_Kanji_assassin
content:
A human individual was an assassin in Kanjiklub from the Outer Rim world Nar Kanji. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, the assassin sought revenge on the Pyke Syndicate gangster Omel Sampak after he ordered the bombing of a Nar Kanji fight school, which killed a number of students as they slept. The assassin was one of many who traveled to the space station Accretion Disco to kill Sampak as he celebrated his victory.
Whilst they were unsuccessful in their attempts to kill Sampak, the assassin did encounter the former pit fighter Tasu Leech, a fellow native of Nar Kanji, who the assassin recognized. The assassin attempted to persuade Leech to join with them, but was unsuccessful. Before departing, the assassin revealed to Leech the true extent of Sampak's attack, which caused Leech to kill Sampak himself.
